Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, fortress guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!!\N--Imprison him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... She thought that it'd be\Nsafer for me to be with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might've been better if I didn't check into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that there's only one escape route...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Daring Luffy and Sanji!\NTheir Great Rescue Operation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the Straw Hat Pirates\Nthat we already captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a man wearing a uniform\Nwho pretended to be a Navy officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! You can report it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you see suspicious individuals,\Nimprison them immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?! That long-nosed guy\Nwas a crew member of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But why did he take\Nthe trouble to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. In the bay, there're lots of\Nships that are better than this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could've taken one\Nof them and quickly escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how stupid pirates are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you already done\Nfor the day, Mechao-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slave-drive an elderly man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's "elderly"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn idiot! At least try to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... This is such a complicated fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Zoro and Usopp are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since they got caught,\Nthey were probably sent to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then we'll go to the jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where the jail is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that belly button island\Nis suspicious after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno, I just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in any case, that sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's surrounded by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, the only way to\Nescape is to cross that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain, but I guess we should go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Going the way we\Ncame is also gonna be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! This is District 4 in Block F. All clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in contact with each other\Nusing Mini Transponder Snails.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't gonna be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, Sanji.\N--Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kinda exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving already, you damn monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Port Entry Records"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange. There're times when\Nno ships enter or leave. Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told us over and over on our way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Special Inspector\NMajor Shepherd, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that, get me\Nout of here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have business with Commander Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Shepherd?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, I see! This is the guy\NRobin was pretending to be!\N--Enough of your nonsense! There's no way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So they've mistaken him for one of us instead!\N--a Navy major from Headquarters would\Nlet his ID and his coat be stolen so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop it now. It's disgraceful!\N--Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:07:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man should know when to\Ngive up! Let's not struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my comrade, Condoriano...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Condoriano?! What's that?!\NWho the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... Stop making bad jokes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect us to believe you've\Nforgotten my face or your own name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't come near me! I'm not your buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know him! I don't know this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow... What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Did the impact from the fall\Ncause you to lose your memory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad... It's too sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Please! Would you let at least him out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the same Condoriano that I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There isn't even a\Npoint in interrogating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean, "that settles it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What're you going to do with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't you get that\NI'm telling you to wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Condoriano!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Condoriano?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice move, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went well! You should thank me, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look creepy, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there still haven't been any reports\Nof the other Straw Hats being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Commander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably having a\Nhard time finding the jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead of them and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure not to act hastily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we ensure our\Nvictory by making the first move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I guess we have to\Nforce our way through after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's unguarded down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Luffy! We'll head down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one we captured earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turned out to be a Straw Hat member\Nwhose name is Condoriano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Condoriano?\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He insists that he's Major Shepherd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we think that it's clearly a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there're two Shepherds, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro... Don't you\Nthink this is kinda strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It gives me a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Mechao-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What're you doing in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I...? I just had\Na little matter to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull them back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not with you! I need to talk to\Nthat long-nose held captive there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! Wait! I can't let you\Ntalk to a prisoner so freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long. Cut me some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Ah! You're the guy from...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me something\Nhappened to the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Your ship is okay... for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who\Nrepaired that ship, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you did it isn't acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you use splices,\Neven if you nail the iron sheets,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll break in no time when\Nstrong winds blow, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splices?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't even know what splices are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually, I'm not a maintenance\Nman or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that did those repairs was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone did them in just one night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That was when we were\Nin a place called a sky island
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that was 10,000 meters up in the sky, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? 10,000, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah... You probably\Ndon't believe it anyway, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that ship\Nfell from the sky, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You believe me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I saw it with my own eyes,\NI have to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the angle at which it fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it probably fell from a\Nconsiderable height, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! We had a really\Nhard time on the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was God and there were\Nangels... It was really tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God and angels?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk as if you died once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Far from just once, there were\Ntons of times that I thought I'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, about what you told me earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it foggy the night that this someone\Nwho repaired the ship appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Exactly! How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you, by any chance,\Nknow who that was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh-What're you doing?!\N--That's it, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're quite busy with various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Escort him out.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Hey! Tell me who that was!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I forgot to tell\Nyou something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, long-nose! When you repair the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pay attention to the areas\Nthat you usually don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those areas are often the\Nones most in need of repair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you treasure your ship, don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I got it, old man! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone just came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But that place really is fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then shall we go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! This is a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We arrived here after we\Ntook the deserted route.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if they're telling us where\NZoro and Usopp are... Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! The fortress guy is a nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap. A trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably trying to save\Ntime and send us straight into jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we can't rescue Zoro\Nand Usopp unless we go inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Why would we want to get\Ntrapped by our enemy so easil--?! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that it'd be better than wasting\Ntime wandering around aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also worried about\NNami-san and Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, are you thinking it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You did, didn't you?!\N--I said I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, get moving already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Usopp! Where're you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you hear Luffy's voice just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really Luffy! Hey, Luffy! We're right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you wanna do that?\NThose guys can hear too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, don't come!\NNo, I changed my mind! Come get us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me. Tell them to come\Nif they want to or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come if you want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... They came...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I'll get you... out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! This is the Sea Prism Stone's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender obediently, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! You are making light of us, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's enough to stop us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this still not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the same to me, idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! It's painful to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bars can't be broken unless\Nyou use a cannon or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! These bars sure are tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannon...? Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take what's inside my pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pocket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an Impact Dial in there.\NUse it to break these bars!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impact Dial... Hey, it causes\Npain to the user, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to worry about that!\NNow, take it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they talking about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up gracefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wait a sec, gorilla man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something remarkable,\Nso keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A seashell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be my fault if you\Nget hurt standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This well-tempered snake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That total moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Are you trying to\Ntell us that's your secret weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Or I'll gut you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yipes, he's scary! A backlash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Um, Sanji-kun, sorry!\NIt's actually in the other pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. It's this side. This side... This...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flavor... It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell stored a fart in my Flavor Dial?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I didn't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! It's gonna explode! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion in the jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape... successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ouch!!\N--Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! What a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there's no point staying here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty! Guys, get out of here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Hey, hey! Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Zoro go first! It won't\Nbe my fault if we get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Those who\Ncan move, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go after the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools! Our men should\Nbe in place outside by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll attack them from both sides and\Nsend them to the netherworld this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! We're lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where are we?!\N--How can you get lost?! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! I'm sorry!\NI failed to catch Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the other members?\NAre Roronoa and the others with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witnesses told me that they didn't\Nsee Condoriano with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Lt. Commander,\Nthe bridge is guarded, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Well, don't be so discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll still have many\Nopportunities to catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like those kids made their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get moving towards the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move ahead, pursuing our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the answers are right here, pouring out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rush forth, rush forth,\Non the road opened before us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep moving forward! We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give in, we won't give in,\Neven if the obstacle is big
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be scared of,\Nwe can overcome it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means something fun might happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.88,0:23:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, worrying about annoying crap is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.55,0:23:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see what kind of trap it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think you can escape\Nfrom Navarone? And from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get caught! We're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter the Hot-Blooded Special Forces!\NBattle on the Bridge!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
